<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>باب مُطَهَّر ومُطَيْر<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥٤١٣]</span> مُطَهَّر بن الهَيْثَم <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روى عن:</span> عَلْقَمَة بن أبي جَمرة الضُّبَعيِّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روى عنه:</span> عبَّاد بن الوليد.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قال ابن أبي حاتم:</span> روى عن المثنى بن سعيد، ومحمد بن ثابت البنانيِّ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روى عنه:</span> محمد بن مرزوق.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روي له:</span> ابن ماجه.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٥٤١٤]</span> مُطَيْر والد سُلَيْم <span style="color:#008000">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روى عن:</span> ذي الزَّوائد.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روى عنه:</span> ابنه سليم.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روي له:</span> أبو داود.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>* * *<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) "تهذيب الكمال" (٢٨/ ٨٨).<br>(٢) "تهذيب الكمال" (٢٨/ ٩٠).</p> </div>